OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772062284
OL,3,CMan arrested after eight people
OL,4,Cinjured in head-on crash
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after eight
OL,7,Fpeople were injured in a head-on crash
OL,8,Fon the A1 in Northumberland.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a report of a
OL,11,Ftwo-vehicle collision on the
OL,12,Fsouthbound carriageway at Rosebrough,
OL,13,Fsouth of Purdey Lodge and north of
OL,14,FBrowniside, at 7.30pm on Saturday (21
OL,15,FFebruary).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
