PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772062284
OL,3,CMan arrested after eight people
OL,4,Cinjured in head-on crash
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police said it was
OL,7,Freported that a blue Audi Q3 had been
OL,8,Ftravelling north when it entered the
OL,9,Fsouthbound carriageway and collided
OL,10,Fhead on with a silver Mitsubishi
OL,11,FMirage car which was travelling south.
OL,13,FEight people ` three who were in the
OL,14,FMitsubishi and five who were in the
OL,15,FAudi ` were taken to hospital for
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,FThe force confirmed on Monday that
OL,19,Fseven of those who went to hospital
OL,20,Fhad been discharged.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772062284
OL,3,CMan arrested after eight people
OL,4,Cinjured in head-on crash
OL,6,FOne of the eight injured ` a man in
OL,7,Fhis 40s who was a passenger in the
OL,8,FMitsubishi ` suffered serious injuries
OL,9,Fand remains in hospital in a stable
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FBoth vehicles were left with
OL,13,Fsignificant damage following the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FA section of the road remained closed
OL,17,Ffor several hours to allow officers to
OL,18,Fcarry out enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
