OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772062284
OL,3,CMan arrested after eight people
OL,4,Cinjured in head-on crash
OL,6,FOfficers with Northumbria Police's
OL,7,FRoads Police Unit (RPU) continue to
OL,8,Finvestigate the crash and a 37-year-
OL,9,Fold man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,10,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving.
OL,13,FHe has been released on police bail
OL,14,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,16,FPolice are appealing to anyone who
OL,17,Fwitnessed the moments leading up to
OL,18,Fthe collision to contact the force.
OL,19,FThey are particularly keen to hear
OL,20,Ffrom anyone who has dash cam footage.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
